node.text: First of all. I’m picking one person to give $100 to in the comments that tells me how this video touched their heart and shares it on their stories. Second of all, more importantly...don’t let your loyalty become your slavery. Don’t let your “loyalty” be the reason you stay miserable the rest of your life. Be loyal to those that deserve it! Be loyal to those that give you that same type of respect back. TAG someone to this video that needs it! And text me 817.242.2719 if this touched your heart. #trentshelton #loyalty #inspiration

node.text:
$100 to the person who can guess what I told @miketyson lol

Can’t lie..I felt like the dude on Coming to America “Oh my gosh it’s really you, I will cherish this moment for the rest of my life” 😂

Legendary moment! 

#trentshelton #miketyson

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by T R E N T S H E L T O N on August 22, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Dear God: feel lost, guide me. feel weak, strengthen me. feel hurt, heal me. Please be my peace in my pain, and be my shelter in my storm. Amen. -@TrentShelton'.

node.text:
Drop a 🙏🏾 if you need(ed) this prayer.

Not a single soul is immune to struggle. We all will have our experiences with hard times. Check on people. Some of those closest to you might be fighting a silent battle that you don’t even know about.

Let the lord be thy Shelter 🙏🏾. 

Comment your struggle and lets all get in the comment thread and help each other. 

#prayer #god #love #mentalhealth

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by T R E N T S H E L T O N on August 21, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Trent Shelton @TrentShelton Just because you're strong enough to handle the pain, doesn't mean you deserve it.'.

node.text:
Put a ❤️ if you feel this! 

Stop carrying unnecessary baggage. Let it go.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by T R E N T S H E L T O N on August 18, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Dear God: I have no idea where you are taking me, but I trust you.'.

node.text:
🙏🏾 if you TRUST GOD! 

Lets be real, it can be hard to trust when you don’t understand. It can be hard to trust when it doesn’t make sense. BUT that’s what faith is! Trusting God DESPITE….DESPITE what it looks like, seems like, or what it could be like. You know that God got a plan to prosper you through it all. Hold on to your faith my friend, and let go of those burdens. 

SAVE THIS TO REMIND YOURSELF IN THOSE STORMS!

node.text:
𝘋𝘳𝘰𝘱 𝘢 🙏🏾 𝘐𝘧 𝘺𝘰𝘶 𝘧𝘦𝘦𝘭 𝘵𝘩𝘪𝘴.⁣
⁣
𝐂𝐨𝐦𝐦𝐞𝐧𝐭 👇 𝐡𝐨𝐰 𝐫𝐞𝐦𝐨𝐯𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐲𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐬𝐞𝐥𝐟 𝐟𝐫𝐨𝐦 𝐭𝐨𝐱𝐢𝐜 𝐬𝐢𝐭𝐮𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧𝐬 𝐡𝐚𝐬 𝐡𝐞𝐥𝐩𝐞𝐝 𝐲𝐨𝐮𝐫 𝐥𝐢𝐟𝐞⁣
⁣
•𝐑𝐄𝐇𝐀𝐁 𝐒𝐄𝐒𝐒𝐈𝐎𝐍•⁣
Sometimes it’s necessary in your life to “UNPLUG” from situations that’s doing nothing but connecting you to pain, stress, and anger. People might call you difficult because you choose not to stay connected to something that isn’t for your life. Always remember, there’s nothing wrong with prioritizing your peace and having enough self-awareness to know that something is toxic for your life. ⁣
⁣
𝘛𝘈𝘎 𝘈 𝘍𝘙𝘐𝘌𝘕𝘋 𝘛𝘏𝘈𝘛 𝘕𝘌𝘌𝘋𝘚 𝘛𝘖 𝘚𝘌𝘌 𝘛𝘏𝘐𝘚

node.text:
𝘐 𝘯𝘦𝘦𝘥 𝘺𝘰𝘶 𝘵𝘰 𝘋𝘳𝘰𝘱 𝘢 🙏🏾 𝘐𝘧 𝘺𝘰𝘶 𝘬𝘯𝘰𝘸 𝘵𝘩𝘪𝘴 𝘪𝘴 𝘵𝘳𝘶𝘦. ⁣⁣
⁣
Drop a 𝐜𝐨𝐦𝐦𝐞𝐧𝐭 👇🏾 with an upgrade 𝐆𝐨𝐝 blessed you with!!! ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
•𝐑𝐞𝐡𝐚𝐛 𝐒𝐞𝐬𝐬𝐢𝐨𝐧• ⁣⁣
I need you to understand sometimes you have to lose certain things, so God can bless you with better things. Certain things HAVE TO end so better things can begin. The storm never makes sense until you see the growth it produced. ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
Remember, sometimes the best way to add to your life is to subtract from it 🤷🏾‍♂️⁣⁣
⁣⁣
⁣
#trentshelton #faith #rehabtime #god #blessings #blessed #relationshipquotes #love #confidence #fortworth #texas #loveyourself #real
